Aricalculator - Tools
=====================
This is the tool chain for the AriCalculator project.

HSW12
-----
Assembler and IDE

Update Subprojects
------------------
A shell script to keep all subprojects up to date.

Test Builder
------------
A set of Perl scripts to compile the source code and wrap the resulting S-Record
into command files which can be executed by a D-Bug12(X) debugger.

Image Converter
---------------
This Perl script converts a grayscale image into a sequence of B/W frames and
generates ASM tables and compressed command sequences for the DISP module.

Dictionary Tree Generator
-------------------------
A Perl script to generate a dictionary search tree for S12CForth.
